text: haey( chaur changcha) nowpel del yeung ban dak kechchasanyea leu ambaur aisreael tha puok anak min trauv korp sakkar champoh anak na krawpi a l laoh laey haey trauv thveula champoh meateabeta ning nheatesandean ning ke m ng kamprea ning anak kreikr ning trauv niyeay sdei laocha muoy mnoussaalok ning trauv brate b tde sa lat haeyning trauv brichcheak hsaa kat . banteabmk puok anak ban berchenh( pi kechchasanyea) leuklengte muoychamnuon tauch knongchamnaom puok anak bonnaoh khn del puok anakchea anak berchenh
